---
import TestPage from "../layouts/TestPage.astro";
---

<TestPage
  title="Centro de Soporte – Cuaderno de Campo Digital"
  heading="Impulso y Soporte Técnico"
  description="Accede a recursos oficiales, guías de digitalización y soporte especializado para tu explotación."
  variant="ayudas"
  layoutType="suspended"
  image="/images/ayudas/customer_support_agri.png"
>
  <div class="subpage-content">

    <div class="support-categories">
      <div class="category-block glass">
        <div class="cat-icon">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"></path><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"></polyline><line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"></line><line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"></line><polyline points="10 9 9 9 8 9"></polyline></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Kit Digital</h3>
        <p>Como agentes digitalizadores homologados, te ayudamos a canjear tu bono en soluciones de agricultura inteligente.</p>
        <a href="/ayudas/kit-digital" class="partner-link">Ver Soluciones Kit Digital →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="category-block glass">
        <div class="cat-icon">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"></line><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Subvenciones</h3>
        <p>Información sobre fondos europeos, PERTE y ayudas autonómicas para la modernización de maquinaria.</p>
        <a href="/ayudas/digitalizacion" class="partner-link">Explorar Ayudas →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="category-block glass">
        <div class="cat-icon">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Centro de Ayuda</h3>
        <p>Tutoriales interactivos, guías de uso de sensores y asistencia técnica personalizada de agrónomos.</p>
        <a href="/ayudas/soporte" class="partner-link">Acceder a Soporte →</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="video-tutorials glass">
      <h2 style="color: #FFFFFF;">Formación Directa</h2>
      <p style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);">Aprende a usar la plataforma en menos de lo que tardas en revisar tu finca.</p>
      <div class="video-grid">
        <div class="video-item">
          <div class="video-thumb" style="background-image: url('/images/ayudas/customer_support_agri.png')">
              <div class="play-btn">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="white" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="5 3 19 12 5 21 5 3"></polygon></svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <span>Introducción a la plataforma</span>
        </div>
        <div class="video-item">
          <div class="video-thumb" style="background-image: url('/images/ayudas/sensor_iot_tutorial.png')">
              <div class="play-btn">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="white" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="5 3 19 12 5 21 5 3"></polygon></svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <span>Configuración de sensores IoT</span>
        </div>
        <div class="video-item">
          <div class="video-thumb" style="background-image: url('/images/sinergias/fieldbee_autoguiado.png')">
              <div class="play-btn">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="white" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="5 3 19 12 5 21 5 3"></polygon></svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <span>Gestión de Cuaderno SIEX</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</TestPage>

<style>
  .support-categories {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 30px;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
  }

  .category-block {
    background: white;
    padding: 40px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.03);
    transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .category-block:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-turquoise);
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  }

  .cat-icon {
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    background: rgba(15, 181, 174, 0.1);
    border-radius: 16px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    color: var(--color-turquoise-dark);
  }

  .category-block h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    color: var(--color-gray-900);
  }

  .category-block p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .partner-link {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-turquoise-dark);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .video-tutorials {
    background: var(--color-gray-900);
    color: white;
    padding: 60px;
    border-radius: 40px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .video-tutorials h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .video-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 30px;
    margin-top: 40px;
  }

  .video-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 15px;
    color: #FFFFFF; /* High contrast for labels */
  }

  .video-thumb {
    aspect-ratio: 16/9;
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    border-radius: 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .video-thumb::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    transition: background 0.3s ease;
  }

  .video-thumb:hover::after {
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
  }

  .play-btn {
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    background: var(--color-turquoise);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 24px;
    z-index: 2;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .video-thumb:hover .play-btn {
    transform: scale(1.1);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .intro-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
